{"tid":1568684,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"入嚟睇吓藍方部署","createTime":"2019-09-14T10:54:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T11:28:38.000Z","uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"23e586bf06c7fb5853b5009f7c4193537688f70c","tid":1568684,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:54:35.000Z","msg":"藍絲遊行，有黑警伴隨&gt; 搞連儂 引和理非，勇武，街坊出黎&gt;打人，一還手就淨係拉佢地<br />\n<br />\n遇上咁樣做有兩個目的<br />\n1.跑數<br />\n2.阻嚇和理非<br />\n<br />\n最好嘅做法就係冷處理<br />\n拆牆由佢拆，遲啲再起過<br />\n想拉人？現場只有街坊<br />\n留返啲人力物力響我地主場既時候發揮<br />\n黑警鬥街坊其實係增加緊成立委員會既籌碼<br />\n<br />\n所以大家適當時候真係要忍手"},{"pid":"6f0b1a2f10828cbc8cfbbbc980901f58cce3933e","tid":1568684,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:55:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da03c9a916e0f49c4131f364573071300dd16a72","tid":1568684,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:28:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GrxoPEb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGrxoPEb.png&h=884ada0a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}